          <td align="center">
          	          	<div style="display:inline; margin:0px 0px 0px 10px; width:auto; float:left; text-align:left;">
          	  <span class="gn13b">[1937-2 台灣教會公報 文類-散文 作者-許水露/Khó͘ Chuí-lō͘]</span>
          	            	  <br />
          	  <span class="be13b"><a href="artical-5484.htm">六十六卷的聖冊 [ La̍k-cha̍p-la̍k koàn ê Sèng-chheh ]</a></span>
